that suppresses Ziqing.

287
00:25:41,880 --> 00:25:43,210
Did the book mention

288
00:25:44,670 --> 00:25:46,350
how to break the Barrier?

289
00:25:46,350 --> 00:25:48,040
This book didn't say,

290
00:25:48,040 --> 00:25:48,880
but

291
00:25:49,070 --> 00:25:50,410
the book recorded

292
00:25:50,910 --> 00:25:52,380
that the Barrier was set by Meng Tribe.

293
00:25:53,070 --> 00:25:54,920
Yes, I also heard it from my father.

294
00:25:54,920 --> 00:25:57,160
The Meng Tribe of Nanzhao

295
00:25:57,160 --> 00:25:58,600
is the most skilled
in Barrier Technique.

296
00:25:58,600 --> 00:25:59,280
Your Highness,

297
00:25:59,280 --> 00:26:01,260
Meng Tribe has been secluded
in Nanzhao for years

298
00:26:01,880 --> 00:26:03,430
without contact with the outside world.

299
00:26:03,430 --> 00:26:05,710
