summons them, they might not come.

300
00:26:05,710 --> 00:26:07,470
No matter how difficult it is,
we must invite them here.

301
00:26:07,470 --> 00:26:08,310
Yes.

302
00:26:08,790 --> 00:26:09,630
Shadow.

303
00:26:10,150 --> 00:26:10,990
Here.

304
00:26:13,240 --> 00:26:14,830
You must help me

305
00:26:14,830 --> 00:26:15,670
bring Meng Tribe here.

306
00:26:17,150 --> 00:26:17,990
Yes.

307
00:26:23,600 --> 00:26:24,440
Beiyue.

308
00:26:32,070 --> 00:26:33,980
Han Ziqing fell into the Barrier,

309
00:26:34,390 --> 00:26:36,620
and the entrance disappeared
out of thin air?

310
00:26:37,390 --> 00:26:38,230
What is going on?

311
00:26:39,120 --> 00:26:40,500
I can't figure it out either.

312
00:26:41,000 --> 00:26:42,040
After all,

313
00:26:42,040 --> 00:26:43,740
I don't know much about Barriers.

314
00:26:46,190 --> 00:26:47,530
It's good that it disappeared.

315
00:26:48,840 --> 00:26:51,330
Let her fend for herself there.

316
00:26:52,270 --> 00:26:53,110
This way,

317
00:26:53,640 --> 00:26:54,640
we can also avoid trouble

318
00:26:54,640 --> 00:26:56,410
with Jun Beiyue.

319
00:26:58,070 --> 00:26:59,410
I think it's unwise.

320
00:27:00,670 --> 00:27:03,260
If we ignore it,

321
00:27:03,720 --> 00:27:06,290
and someone else gets ahead of us,

322
00:27:06,720 --> 00:27:08,380
it will be endless trouble.

323
00:27:09,670 --> 00:27:10,880
I believe

324
00:27:10,880 --> 00:27:12,680
we must find Han Ziqing.

325
00:27:12,680 --> 00:27:14,740
To see the person or her corpse.

326
00:27:15,150 --> 00:27:16,210
Only then can we be at ease.

327
00:27:16,960 --> 00:27:18,170
You are right.

328
00:27:20,550 --> 00:27:23,170
Then we need to find someone to help.

329
00:27:23,840 --> 00:27:25,930
Now there is someone who can be used.

330
00:27:27,840 --> 00:27:29,260
Whom are you referring to?

331
00:27:30,150 --> 00:27:31,880
I have kept her confined in Ice Pool

332
00:27:31,880 --> 00:27:33,050
for over 20 years.

333
00:27:33,910 --> 00:27:34,750
Back then,

334
00:27:35,240 --> 00:27:36,290
she was extraordinarily gifted.

335
00:27:36,910 --> 00:27:39,280
She deciphered the second level
of Meng Tribe's Momentary Tower

336
00:27:39,280 --> 00:27:40,210
stole the true teachings,

337
00:27:40,840 --> 00:27:42,570
and was thus expelled from Meng Tribe.

338
00:27:43,670 --> 00:27:46,590
