339
00:27:46,590 --> 00:27:47,430
I'm afraid...

340
00:27:48,640 --> 00:27:50,570
This woman is ambitious.

341
00:27:51,190 --> 00:27:52,290
Releasing her

342
00:27:53,840 --> 00:27:54,930
might ruin our grand plans.

343
00:27:55,670 --> 00:27:56,510
Yes,

344
00:27:57,480 --> 00:27:58,860
you are right.

345
00:27:59,760 --> 00:28:00,830
Then it's better

346
00:28:00,830 --> 00:28:02,780
not to get her involved for now.

347
00:28:05,760 --> 00:28:08,830
Now we have no choice
but to seek help from Meng Tribe.

348
00:28:08,830 --> 00:28:11,680
But Chief Meng has always been stubborn.

349
00:28:11,680 --> 00:28:13,350
He is unwilling to associate
with the royal family.

350
00:28:13,350 --> 00:28:15,640
Even if he can find the Barrier

351
00:28:15,640 --> 00:28:16,690
and open the entrance,

352
00:28:17,150 --> 00:28:19,210
he probably won't follow our orders.

353
00:28:21,390 --> 00:28:22,810
No matter how powerful they are,

354
00:28:23,430 --> 00:28:25,160
they are still citizens of Nanzhao.

355
00:28:25,160 --> 00:28:26,000
Yes.

356
00:28:29,310 --> 00:28:30,330
Besides Chief Meng,

357
00:28:31,520 --> 00:28:32,830
there might be other disciples

358
00:28:32,830 --> 00:28:35,160
in Meng Tribe who can handle it.

359
00:28:35,160 --> 00:28:38,350
It is said that Chief Meng
is quite dissatisfied

360
00:28:38,350 --> 00:28:40,980
with his two sons.

361
00:28:41,600 --> 00:28:45,380
He believes they are mediocre
and behave improperly.

362
00:28:45,760 --> 00:28:48,210
Therefore, he hasn't considered them

363
00:28:48,840 --> 00:28:50,190
to be the next chief.

364
00:28:50,190 --> 00:28:51,500
