365
00:28:52,520 --> 00:28:53,640
We might as well

366
00:28:53,640 --> 00:28:55,020
make some moves in this matter

367
00:28:55,430 --> 00:28:56,980
and lend them a helping hand.

368
00:29:14,000 --> 00:29:16,330
Greetings, Your Majesty.

369
00:29:16,880 --> 00:29:17,810
You may rise.

370
00:29:18,550 --> 00:29:19,470
Thank you, Your Majesty.

371
00:29:19,470 --> 00:29:20,310
Thank you, Your Majesty.

372
00:29:23,070 --> 00:29:23,910
Your Majesty,

373
00:29:24,480 --> 00:29:26,740
it has been a long time
since we last visited the Royal City.

374
00:29:27,120 --> 00:29:28,570
Please forgive us, Your Majesty.

375
00:29:29,520 --> 00:29:30,800
Masters,

376
00:29:30,800 --> 00:29:33,020
you must have received my secret letter.

377
00:29:37,000 --> 00:29:38,500
