379
00:29:41,230 --> 00:29:42,410
to alleviate your worries.

380
00:29:43,000 --> 00:29:46,260
However, my father is quite averse

381
00:29:47,150 --> 00:29:48,290
to the matters outside the tribe,

382
00:29:49,430 --> 00:29:50,810
and is unwilling to get involved.

383
00:29:52,030 --> 00:29:54,800
If we act behind his back,

384
00:29:54,800 --> 00:29:56,620
it would be against the tribe's rules.

385
00:29:57,760 --> 00:29:59,620
Masters, your words are mistaken.

386
00:30:00,240 --> 00:30:02,280
Compared to the rules
of Meng Tribe,

387
00:30:02,280 --> 00:30:04,530
the safety of Nanzhao is more important.

388
00:30:05,190 --> 00:30:06,050
Moreover,

389
00:30:06,550 --> 00:30:08,380
when this Poisonous Grass World
was established,

390
00:30:08,840 --> 00:30:11,290
your ancestor chief
was also involved.

391
00:30:12,430 --> 00:30:13,800
Now,

392
00:30:13,800 --> 00:30:15,230
it is only natural

393
00:30:15,230 --> 00:30:17,160
for his descendants

394
00:30:17,160 --> 00:30:18,690
to find and open this Barrier.

395
00:30:20,720 --> 00:30:22,740
Therefore, I persuaded my brother

396
00:30:23,240 --> 00:30:26,190
to come here
without informing our father.

397
00:30:26,190 --> 00:30:29,100
Even if we are punished
for violating the rules,

398
00:30:30,070 --> 00:30:32,760
my brother and I
will have a clear conscience.

399
00:30:32,760 --> 00:30:33,600
Brother.

400
00:30:35,640 --> 00:30:37,660
Third Master, I'm pleased

401
00:30:38,070 --> 00:30:39,620
that you can understand
for the greater good.

402
00:30:41,270 --> 00:30:43,830
I promise,

403
00:30:43,830 --> 00:30:47,050
as long as you can find the entrance
to the Poisonous Grass World,

404
00:30:47,520 --> 00:30:48,530
and find the person,

405
00:30:49,070 --> 00:30:52,000
I will fully support Second Master

406
00:30:52,000 --> 00:30:53,410
to take over Meng Tribe.

407
00:30:54,150 --> 00:30:54,990
Brother.

408
00:30:59,240 --> 00:31:03,070
Your Majesty, I will do my utmost
to relieve your worries.

409
00:31:03,070 --> 00:31:03,910
Thank you, Your Majesty.

410
00:31:04,670 --> 00:31:05,510
You may rise.

411
00:31:06,520 --> 00:31:07,360
Thank you, Your Majesty.

412
00:31:09,720 --> 00:31:10,560
Remember,

413
00:31:12,030 --> 00:31:13,620
once you capture Han Ziqing,

414
00:31:14,070 --> 00:31:16,450
kill her immediately.

415
00:31:24,240 --> 00:31:25,410
Mr. Situ,

416
00:31:25,880 --> 00:31:28,690
have you heard from Shadow
in Dream Island?

417
00:31:29,240 --> 00:31:30,080
Shadow has sent a letter.

418
00:31:30,880 --> 00:31:31,720
