419
00:31:32,120 --> 00:31:34,880
He says Chief Meng is old and reclusive,

420
00:31:34,880 --> 00:31:36,430
and has long stopped
seeing outside guests.

421
00:31:36,430 --> 00:31:37,880
He is still waiting outside

422
00:31:37,880 --> 00:31:38,990
and he asks us to wait for news.

423
00:31:40,840 --> 00:31:43,620
That's all we can do for now.

424
00:31:44,600 --> 00:31:47,040
How about I write a letter to my father

425
00:31:47,040 --> 00:31:48,530
and see if he has any ideas?

426
00:31:49,520 --> 00:31:50,500
That would be great.

427
00:31:50,880 --> 00:31:51,720
Thank you.

428
00:32:03,240 --> 00:32:04,470
I have followed the steps

429
00:32:04,470 --> 00:32:06,450
to meticulously create
this little soul bug.

430
00:32:07,070 --> 00:32:08,830
I rely on you to find the Barrier now.

431
00:32:08,830 --> 00:32:10,110
You must not let me down.

432
00:32:10,110 --> 00:32:11,380
Don't give up halfway.

433
00:32:14,760 --> 00:32:16,410
Right. I should follow you.

434
00:33:12,550 --> 00:33:13,930
(I can't be trapped here.)

435
00:33:15,070 --> 00:33:16,290
(I still need to find the music scores.)

436
00:33:17,000 --> 00:33:17,980
