440
00:33:53,360 --> 00:33:54,780
That's quite strange.

441
00:33:55,960 --> 00:33:56,980
What's so strange about it?

442
00:33:59,240 --> 00:34:00,980
Although the entrance has moved,

443
00:34:02,150 --> 00:34:04,140
I can still sense it.

444
00:34:05,880 --> 00:34:07,100
It should be nearby.

445
00:34:10,390 --> 00:34:11,230
Take this.

446
00:34:22,280 --> 00:34:23,120
This way.

447
00:35:00,340 --> 00:35:03,260
(Dream Island)

448
00:35:17,590 --> 00:35:18,430
Don't move.

449
00:35:18,480 --> 00:35:19,380
Who are you?

450
00:35:19,560 --> 00:35:20,970
How dare you trespass on Dream Island?

451
00:35:24,280 --> 00:35:26,770
I am the Crown Prince of Dongling.

452
00:35:27,520 --> 00:35:29,290
I have something urgent to discuss
with Chief Meng.

453
00:35:30,320 --> 00:35:31,570
The Crown Prince of Dongling

454
00:35:32,670 --> 00:35:33,660
has something urgent

455
00:35:34,800 --> 00:35:35,640
to discuss

456
00:35:37,110 --> 00:35:38,330
with Chief Meng.

457
00:35:43,520 --> 00:35:44,360
Master,

458
00:35:44,480 --> 00:35:46,700
that person has been unconscious
since arriving on the island.

459
00:35:47,590 --> 00:35:49,190
He claimed to be the Crown Prince
of Dongling

460
00:35:49,190 --> 00:35:50,460
and had something to discuss with you.

461
00:35:50,910 --> 00:35:52,280
But you have been in seclusion,

462
00:35:52,280 --> 00:35:53,530
so I didn't dare disturb you.

463
00:36:18,910 --> 00:36:19,860
Give him some water.

464
00:36:43,670 --> 00:36:44,510
Who are you?

465
00:36:45,480 --> 00:36:46,490
Young man,

466
00:36:46,910 --> 00:36:49,530
your health doesn't seem very good.

467
00:36:51,350 --> 00:36:53,010
I am well aware of my illness.

468
00:36:53,590 --> 00:36:54,860
It is beyond cure.

469
00:36:55,320 --> 00:36:56,620
Just let it be.

470
00:36:57,720 --> 00:36:59,730
May I ask if you are Chief Meng?

471
00:37:00,110 --> 00:37:01,660
Yes, I am.

472
00:37:03,720 --> 00:37:05,150
Your body is weak.

473
00:37:05,150 --> 00:37:06,100
Don't move.

474
00:37:06,910 --> 00:37:08,190
I am Xuanyuan Lige,

475
00:37:08,190 --> 00:37:09,710
