to ask for your help.

476
00:37:09,710 --> 00:37:10,900
That is why I came here abruptly.

477
00:37:11,390 --> 00:37:13,050
Chief Meng, please save a life.

478
00:37:15,000 --> 00:37:17,120
Are you still caring about
others' affairs?

479
00:37:17,120 --> 00:37:20,700
But you now are on the brink of death.

480
00:37:21,150 --> 00:37:22,760
Compared to my life,

481
00:37:22,760 --> 00:37:24,480
there is something more important
right now.

482
00:37:24,590 --> 00:37:26,320
When you can survive,

483
00:37:26,320 --> 00:37:28,000
we can talk about it later.

484
00:37:28,000 --> 00:37:28,840
How about that?

485
00:37:29,760 --> 00:37:31,040
But Chief Meng,

486
00:37:31,040 --> 00:37:31,880
I...

487
00:37:39,190 --> 00:37:40,900
You are already at the end of your life.

488
00:37:41,630 --> 00:37:44,460
I can only use the Barrier Technique
to save you.

489
00:37:47,350 --> 00:37:49,490
