others' affairs,

490
00:37:50,080 --> 00:37:51,870
but by a stroke of fate,

491
00:37:51,870 --> 00:37:53,570
you came to Meng Tribe.

492
00:37:54,040 --> 00:37:56,380
I cannot stand by and watch you die.

493
00:38:32,670 --> 00:38:33,510
Master.

494
00:38:35,240 --> 00:38:36,460
Take care of him.

495
00:39:20,110 --> 00:39:20,950
This way.

496
00:39:39,300 --> 00:39:40,500
(Sha)

497
00:39:49,760 --> 00:39:51,250
Brother, do you sense anything?

498
00:39:53,870 --> 00:39:55,330
The aura is getting stronger.

499
00:39:57,800 --> 00:39:59,250
It should be right here.

500
00:40:01,830 --> 00:40:02,670
Here?

501
00:40:04,520 --> 00:40:05,420
In this room?

502
00:40:09,190 --> 00:40:11,330
Who are you?
