503
00:40:12,190 --> 00:40:13,320
I...

504
00:40:13,320 --> 00:40:14,320
We are...

505
00:40:14,320 --> 00:40:15,160
What happened?

506
00:40:15,670 --> 00:40:16,520
Mr. Situ,

507
00:40:16,520 --> 00:40:17,770
we found two suspicious individuals.

508
00:40:20,280 --> 00:40:21,360
Who are you?

509
00:40:21,360 --> 00:40:22,200
What are you doing here?

510
00:40:24,480 --> 00:40:26,840
We are from Meng Tribe.

511
00:40:26,840 --> 00:40:27,730
We came here...

512
00:40:28,240 --> 00:40:29,220
You are from Meng Tribe?

513
00:40:29,960 --> 00:40:31,190
