522
00:41:35,390 --> 00:41:36,250
You little bug.

523
00:41:37,240 --> 00:41:38,140
Why did you stop moving?

524
00:41:39,480 --> 00:41:40,490
What are you doing here?

525
00:41:43,110 --> 00:41:43,970
What's going on?

526
00:42:00,110 --> 00:42:01,530
Now here's the current situation.

527
00:42:02,150 --> 00:42:04,010
I wonder if you two can help.

528
00:42:05,590 --> 00:42:07,460
It's not easy to find the Barrier.

529
00:42:07,870 --> 00:42:10,660
We need to sense the aura
of the Barrier first.

530
00:42:11,870 --> 00:42:13,010
Only then can we make a decision.

531
00:42:13,800 --> 00:42:14,660
Mr. Situ,

532
00:42:15,350 --> 00:42:17,050
has Chief Meng arrived?

533
00:42:19,080 --> 00:42:20,320
May I know who are they?

534
00:42:20,320 --> 00:42:21,900
These are the two masters
from Meng Tribe.

535
00:42:23,110 --> 00:42:25,000
We are the seventh-generation disciples
of Meng Tribe.

536
00:42:25,000 --> 00:42:26,710
By the order of my father,

537
00:42:26,710 --> 00:42:28,660
we have come to help Fourth Prince.

538
00:42:29,800 --> 00:42:31,320
That's wonderful.

539
00:42:31,320 --> 00:42:33,430
Earlier, Shadow sent a message

540
00:42:33,430 --> 00:42:35,810
saying Chief Meng was unwilling
to intervene in this matter.

541
00:42:36,520 --> 00:42:38,530
My father is upright by nature,

542
00:42:39,480 --> 00:42:40,900
and he is also a reasonable person.

543
00:42:42,150 --> 00:42:44,950
He can't come here in person,

544
00:42:44,950 --> 00:42:46,900
so he sent us two brothers.

545
00:42:47,430 --> 00:42:48,910
Chief Meng is so righteous.

546
00:42:48,910 --> 00:42:51,670
I want to thank you
on behalf of Fourth Prince.

547
00:42:51,670 --> 00:42:54,800
Since it is Fourth Prince's request,

548
00:42:54,800 --> 00:42:57,010
why not invite him to join us

549
00:42:57,390 --> 00:42:59,770
